Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP47
Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP47.Network.Client

Class NetworkHandlerVisitor

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP47.Network.Client.NetworkHandlerVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visitor
public class NetworkHandlerVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor
This class implements the Visitor interface referred to the Visitor pattern. In this way, every time the NetworkHandler calls an update, he knows exactly what to do thanks to the Visitable class which is passed in.
